replies.body:
Pretty frustrating when you're just trying to enjoy a game of League and your client goes wonky on you! It does sound like your client is having an issue obtaining information from the Server. The first thing I would suggest is putting your client into low spec mode from the game settings. If the issue persists from there it would be a great idea to run through the steps in our [connection guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664)! 

If that fails, reach back out to me and we'll have our tech team dive a little deeper into the issue! 
{{champion:25}}
